<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:11:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国外长在慕尼黑安全会议上警告不要脱钩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-foreign-minister-warns-against-decoupling-munich-security-conference-2024-02-17/</link><description>中国外长王毅警告西方，如果为了降低风险而寻求与中国脱钩，将犯历史性错误。</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 13:11:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-foreign-minister-warns-against-decoupling-munich-security-conference-2024-02-17/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大的清算人准备就审计问题起诉普华永道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/china-evergrandes-liquidators-prepare-sue-pwc-over-audits-ft-reports-2024-02-17/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周六援引知情人士的话报道称，房地产开发商中国恒大的清算人正在准备对其审计师普华永道（PwC）提起潜在诉讼。</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 11:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/china-evergrandes-liquidators-prepare-sue-pwc-over-audits-ft-reports-2024-02-17/</guid></item><item><title>外交部称中国王毅与布林肯在慕尼黑举行“建设性”会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-yi-held-constructive-talks-with-blinken-munich-chinese-foreign-2024-02-17/</link><description>中国外交部周六表示，中国外交部长王毅在慕尼黑安全会议上会见美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯，讨论了取消对中国企业和个人的制裁。</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 03:54:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-yi-held-constructive-talks-with-blinken-munich-chinese-foreign-2024-02-17/</guid></item><item><title>英国卡梅伦向中国外长提出红海和人权问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uks-cameron-raises-red-sea-human-rights-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-2024-02-17/</link><description>英国外交部在一份声明中表示，英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦周五在慕尼黑安全会议上会见了中国外交部长王毅。</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 00:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uks-cameron-raises-red-sea-human-rights-issues-with-chinese-counterpart-2024-02-17/</guid></item><item><title>着眼于中国，美国高级议员誓言支持为太平洋岛屿提供资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eyeing-china-senior-us-lawmaker-vows-back-funding-pacific-islands-2024-02-16/</link><description>美国众议院外交事务委员会共和党主席周五表示，他支持向美国盟友太平洋岛国提供资金，以此作为对抗中国影响力的一种方式，并将推动将其纳入任何补充安全援助法案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 21:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eyeing-china-senior-us-lawmaker-vows-back-funding-pacific-islands-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>意大利监管机构迫使 TikTok 删除“法国疤痕”挑战视频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italy-watchdog-forces-tiktok-remove-french-scar-challenge-videos-2024-02-16/</link><description>意大利通讯当局 AGCOM 周五表示，已迫使社交媒体应用 TikTok 删除一些显示年轻人进行被称为“法国疤痕”的危险行为的视频。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:41:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italy-watchdog-forces-tiktok-remove-french-scar-challenge-videos-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车1月份在中国的交付量增长13%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-boosts-volkswagens-january-deliveries-up-13-2024-02-16/</link><description>大众汽车周五表示，1 月份集团销量增长 13.3%，达到 698,200 辆，其中中国是增长最快的地区。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 12:32:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-boosts-volkswagens-january-deliveries-up-13-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：汇丰银行将改善与香港恒生银行的关系以降低风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-improve-ties-with-hong-kong-unit-hang-seng-mitigate-risk-say-sources-2024-02-16/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，由于担心中国经济逆风加剧和房地产业危机可能导致不良贷款增加，汇丰银行计划加强香港子公司恒生银行的风险管理。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 07:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-improve-ties-with-hong-kong-unit-hang-seng-mitigate-risk-say-sources-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国加强房地产行业“白名单”机制 - 媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-whitelist-mechanism-property-sector-media-2024-02-16/</link><description>据政府支持的媒体澎湃新闻报道，中国五家国有银行已在“白名单”机制下为超过8,200个住宅项目提供开发贷款，旨在为受危机打击的行业注入流动性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-whitelist-mechanism-property-sector-media-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>供应紧张之际，中国将在新加坡航展上展示国产客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</link><description>新加坡将于下周举办自新冠疫情边境限制结束以来首次举办亚洲最大的航空展，地区旅行将出现反弹，展会的军事方面将布满防御系统和紧张的武器买家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-show-off-homegrown-airliner-singapore-air-show-amid-supply-crunch-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>香港当局在价值18亿美元的洗钱案中逮捕了七人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</link><description>香港当局周五表示，他们逮捕了 7 名涉嫌参与 18 亿美元洗钱案件的人，这是该金融中心有史以来规模最大的洗钱案件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-authorities-arrest-seven-18-bln-money-laundering-case-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商押注中国有望重新开放，并向香港大量发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</link><description>根据行业数据和贸易数据，澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商已将数百万瓶葡萄酒运往香港，押注中国将很快取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税并重振价值数亿美元的贸易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 05:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/australian-wine-makers-bet-expected-china-reopening-with-big-shipments-hong-kong-2024-02-16/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋岛国对美国拖延资助感到担忧，对中国发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</link><description>美国的战略盟友太平洋岛国领导人对美国国会预算僵局越来越感到焦虑，这一僵局导致重要的新融资方案的批准被推迟，并警告说，中国正在积极寻求改变他们的忠诚度，包括对台湾的忠诚度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 20:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/anxious-about-us-funding-delay-pacific-island-nations-warn-about-china-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卢比奥敦促 SEC 阻止 Shein IPO，除非披露中国运营风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/rubio-urges-sec-block-shein-ipo-unless-china-operating-risk-disclosed-2024-02-15/</link><description>共和党参议员马可·卢比奥 (Marco Rubio) 要求美国证券交易委员会阻止 Shein 在纽约公开上市的计划，除非这家电子零售商进一步披露其业务运营以及在中国“开展业务的严重风险”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 17:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/rubio-urges-sec-block-shein-ipo-unless-china-operating-risk-disclosed-2024-02-15/</guid></item><item><title>福特和通用汽车首席执行官愿意建立合作伙伴关系以与中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-ceo-open-working-with-rivals-compete-with-china-2024-02-15/</link><description>美国汽车制造商福特和通用汽车的首席执行官周四表示，随着中国竞争对手进军美国和欧洲市场，他们将考虑建立合作伙伴关系，以降低电动汽车技术成本。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 15:12:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ford-ceo-open-working-with-rivals-compete-with-china-2024-02-15/</guid></item></channel></rss>